  "detailed_description": "<strong>Discover the Hidden Hues in Colors</strong><br>Embark on a vibrant puzzle adventure with Colors, where your mission is to uncover the hidden color beneath each square by analyzing the surrounding ambient color ratios.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147830/extras/cc55d027fef2c96c6b87bb7e7486b3ba.avif?t=1725870360\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>Solo Game Play</strong><br>Colors is a solo puzzle game where the challenge lies in deducing a hidden color beneath a square. The key to uncovering it lies in analyzing the color ratios of the surrounding squares.<br><br><strong>Classic and Unique Puzzles</strong><br>Explore a wide range of puzzles that combine ambient color ratios , offering both new and returning players a fresh experience.<br><br><strong>Need Help Getting Started?</strong><br>Learn the basics and advanced strategies in an intuitive tutorial mode designed to help you understanding the idea of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147830/extras/cf98b817baa5e5fcc820ce207c84c95f.avif?t=1725870360\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>Endless Puzzle Fun</strong><br>Replay levels to perfect your strategy, experiment with different difficulty settings, and unlock hidden levels and grow up your stars as a reward for you to dive deeper into the world of Colors.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Discover the Hidden Hues in Colors</strong><br>Embark on a vibrant puzzle adventure with Colors, where your mission is to uncover the hidden color beneath each square by analyzing the surrounding ambient color ratios.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147830/extras/cc55d027fef2c96c6b87bb7e7486b3ba.avif?t=1725870360\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>Solo Game Play</strong><br>Colors is a solo puzzle game where the challenge lies in deducing a hidden color beneath a square. The key to uncovering it lies in analyzing the color ratios of the surrounding squares.<br><br><strong>Classic and Unique Puzzles</strong><br>Explore a wide range of puzzles that combine ambient color ratios , offering both new and returning players a fresh experience.<br><br><strong>Need Help Getting Started?</strong><br>Learn the basics and advanced strategies in an intuitive tutorial mode designed to help you understanding the idea of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147830/extras/cf98b817baa5e5fcc820ce207c84c95f.avif?t=1725870360\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>Endless Puzzle Fun</strong><br>Replay levels to perfect your strategy, experiment with different difficulty settings, and unlock hidden levels and grow up your stars as a reward for you to dive deeper into the world of Colors.",
